Blueberry Cheong

stellanspice.com10 min72 hrs

This syrup is made using a Korean method that turns sugar into fruit syrup. No cooking required, which makes a fresh tasting syrup!

  • 500 g fruit
  • 500 g sugar
  1. Mix fruit and sugar equally in layers
  2. Let on counter if fermentation is wanted
  3. Store in fridge (optionally filter out fruit)
